column5: Would you believe Wind Mill Point...
You were fishing in the Sobeys parking lot and just photoshopped the background...
Behind Mohawk Island, Rock Pt. East of Maitland.
That area on the Canadian side is deadly, where I got my PB smallie!
We have a WINNER....you now will have the pleasure to help clean fish on my next outing....

LOL we call it the dumping grounds,over the years they have dumped tons of slag from the steel plant, snag city LOL! Not a favorite spot for myself,but there is tonns of fish there, and tackle on the bottom!
